	<h1 class="title">Google 要和基因公司合作研发药物，让你活得更久</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/99037/small/99037.jpg?1428742661" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">钟舒婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-28 13:34:26 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/12706/medium/12706.jpg?1438058004" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


